the total sales for
the first row of data,

74
00:03:17,060 --> 00:03:19,720
you can click "cell F2".

75
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:23,690
From there, we'll start
with an equal sign and use

76
00:03:23,690 --> 00:03:28,015
the cell references to input
values in your expression.

77
00:03:28,015 --> 00:03:31,425
We're starting with cell
B2 because the year in

78
