A2 is not a value we want
to add to the total.

79
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:41,460
Then press "Enter."

80
00:03:41,460 --> 00:03:42,815
Just like that,

81
00:03:42,815 --> 00:03:45,730
your total sales has
been calculated for you,

82
00:03:45,730 --> 00:03:47,600
but what if you realized one of

83
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:49,350
the values in your
data was wrong?

84
00:03:49,350 --> 00:03:50,465
No problem.

85
00:03:50,465 --> 00:03:52,900
You can change the
value in any cell using

86
