00:06:16,395 --> 00:06:19,475
Errors can happen at any
stage of data analysis,

123
00:06:19,475 --> 00:06:21,940
and that includes when
you're using spreadsheets.

124
00:06:21,940 --> 00:06:24,630
A formula has to be air tight.

125
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:26,270
If there's something
wrong with one of

126
